{"text": " Welcome to the Silent Mind program, all here is journey towards stability and silence of mind. It is composed of three parts. The first part is accessible to everyone seeking to develop a greater mind-body connection. Part two develops further mental stability whereas part three brings practitioners towards the silence of mind. Each part should be practiced progressively and each stage should be repeated until you are able to practice on your own without guidance. If you're close to our Geneva Center we recommend combining this course with our six-week program which includes on-site practice combined with training on our Silent Mind XR platform. Continuity is what matters and each step is meaningful. Now simply step in and let your Silent Mind journey unfold.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 17.239999999999995, "end": 25.78, "text": " Welcome to the Silent Mind program, all here is journey towards stability and silence", "tokens": [50364, 4027, 281, 264, 40862, 13719, 1461, 11, 439, 510, 307, 4671, 3030, 11826, 293, 12239, 51692], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.3629664872822009, "compression_ratio": 1.0493827160493827, "no_speech_prob": 0.10651573538780212, "words": [{"word": " Welcome", "start": 17.239999999999995, "end": 18.36, "probability": 0.7889618277549744}, {"word": " to", "start": 18.36, "end": 18.66, "probability": 0.9939883947372437}, {"word": " the", "start": 18.66, "end": 18.8, "probability": 0.93598473072052}, {"word": " Silent", "start": 18.8, "end": 19.1, "probability": 0.6478482484817505}, {"word": " Mind", "start": 19.1, "end": 19.38, "probability": 0.9505648016929626}, {"word": " program,", "start": 19.38, "end": 20.02, "probability": 0.5839962363243103}, {"word": " all", "start": 20.66, "end": 21.42, "probability": 0.9627602696418762}, {"word": " here", "start": 21.42, "end": 21.62, "probability": 0.7282624840736389}, {"word": " is", "start": 21.62, "end": 21.8, "probability": 0.7753193974494934}, {"word": " journey"